this family means to me.

00:12.455 --> 00:13.648
Yeah, I understand.

00:13.848 --> 00:15.343
I wanted to ask you about Emma.

00:15.543 --> 00:17.601
- I have her on a list.
- How much does it take?

00:17.801 --> 00:18.736
$20,000.

00:18.936 --> 00:21.103
How much does this run pay?

00:21.303 --> 00:22.886
$25,000.

00:23.684 --> 00:26.042
You know how my
husband was in an accident?

00:26.043 --> 00:26.728
Yeah.

00:26.928 --> 00:29.013
It... it wasn't an accident.

00:29.502 --> 00:30.904
Your son did it.

00:31.104 --> 00:32.584
To family and friends.

00:32.784 --> 00:35.082
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

00:35.083 --> 00:38.351
Your mother asked me if I could come down
and just talk to you for a minute.

00:38.551 --> 00:41.934
Norman, why do you care so much
who your mother might be sleeping with?

00:42.134 --> 00:44.282
